{
  "texts": [
    "Developers and funders should evaluate responsible deployment options and ongoing monitoring for upcoming capability advancements are advised.",
    "For tools scoring 'amber' we recommend case-by-case consideration for follow-up assessment based on:",
    "• The specific misuse-relevant capabilities identified • How the tool fits into existing threat models • Whether the tool represents a novel capability or a marginal improvement over existing tools • Whether the tool could be effectively included in existing evaluation frameworks Successors to amber tools should be assessed, particularly those in categories with high potential for change where technical barriers to advancement are relatively low.",
    "Developers and funders should consider responsible deployment options.",
    "For tools scoring 'Green', no immediate follow-up assessment is required."
  ]
}